parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the third gear transmission can cause a loud clacking or whining noise, which can lead to catastrophic loss of power, transmission lock-up, and potentially cause a crash.
symptoms: Loud clacking or whining noise in third gear
noise is prevalent when downshifting
noise can be heard when accelerating
noise is worse when in third gear only
transmission produces a severe whine and grinding sound
third gear is completely useless
gear has severely worn or is chipped.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden stalling of the engine can cause the motorcycle to lose power, leading to accidents, injuries, or even fatalities, especially when happening at high speeds or in heavy traffic.
symptoms: The engine stops running unexpectedly
often without warning
resulting in a loss of power
stalling
or cutting off while decelerating or accelerating.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of valves, particularly sticking valves, can cause a sudden loss of power, leading to accidents, injuries, or even fatalities, especially when happening at high speeds or in heavy traffic.
symptoms: The engine loses power
hesitates
or stalls
often accompanied by sludge buildup on the valves
sticking valves
or erratic engine performance.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the crank position sensor can cause erratic engine performance, hesitation, or stalling, leading to accidents, injuries, or even fatalities, especially when happening at high speeds or in heavy traffic.
symptoms: The engine hesitates
stalls
or becomes inoperable
often accompanied by erratic acceleration or deceleration.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The intermittent engine stalling can cause the motorcycle to come to an unexpected stop, increasing the risk of accidents, injuries, or fatalities, especially when riding with a passenger.
symptoms: The engine dies or stalls when coming to a stop
downshifting
or engaging the clutch; the motorcycle may stall repeatedly; the clutch pedal feels soft or spongy; the motorcycle may stall at busy intersections or when traffic is approaching from behind.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clutch safety interlock switch can cause the motorcycle to stall unexpectedly, leading to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: The motorcycle stalls when engaging the clutch; the clutch pedal feels soft or spongy; the motorcycle may stall repeatedly; the clutch safety interlock switch may need to be disconnected to prevent stalling.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The ECM mapping issue can cause the motorcycle to stall unexpectedly, leading to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: The motorcycle stalls when coming to a stop or downshifting; the motorcycle may stall repeatedly; the clutch safety interlock switch may need to be disconnected to prevent stalling; the ECM mapping issue may be related to emissions control.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The engine stalling at low speed can cause the motorcycle to lose power and potentially lead to accidents or leave the rider stranded in traffic.
symptoms: The engine dies completely when coming to a stop
frequently after pulling in the clutch
and may occur randomly when exiting a freeway or pulling up to a stoplight.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clutch safety interlock switch can cause the engine to die completely when coming to a stop, potentially leading to accidents or leaving the rider stranded in traffic.
symptoms: The engine dies completely when coming to a stop
frequently after pulling in the clutch
and may occur randomly when exiting a freeway or pulling up to a stoplight.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the speedometer and gauges can cause the rider to lose critical information about the motorcycle's speed and performance, potentially leading to accidents or other safety issues.
symptoms: The speedometer and gauges stop working on a regular basis
and the speedometer may work intermittently.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical connector can cause the motorcycle's lights to fail, potentially leading to accidents or other safety issues, especially at night.
symptoms: The lights fail at night
and the factory crimp connector inside the driving lamps may melt.
